---
title: Mozzarella-Crusted Chicken with Garlic-Roasted Tomatoes and Crispy Potato Wedges
description: Think of this dish as a new take on Chicken Parmesan. Herbs, breadcrumbs, and mozzarella make up a crispy, cheesy coating on juicy chicken. Instead of marinara, garlicky roasted tomatoes add a sweet punch. We’ve added crispy potatoes because, why not?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/de-mozzarella-crusted-chicken-wi-83d3d705.jpg
